{"data":{"id":"ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus","rating":4.9,"websiteUri":"http://www.newyorkheatingsi.com/","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":true,"periods":[{"open":{"day":0,"hour":0,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]},"userRatingCount":111,"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaeU1WYzBjbDloV1RWSlp6SnhOVTQ1VW1sWlNHYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 weeks ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I highly recommend New York Heating and Air Conditioning for all of your heating and cooling needs.  They are very responsive and professional.  Do not hesitate to call them.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I highly recommend New York Heating and Air Conditioning for all of your heating and cooling needs.  They are very responsive and professional.  Do not hesitate to call them.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Jo Ann LoGatto","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103911440666044937683/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLB_U1PEo67OVHE39HSmjBvjtzbUkKuiwYYXV7mNq2VWGGpFw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-25T19:38:49.119952876Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaeU1WYzBjbDloV1RWSlp6SnhOVTQ1VW1sWlNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaeU1WYzBjbDloV1RWSlp6SnhOVTQ1VW1sWlNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c24eb28c90bf0b:0xeb62d03ca65718c8"},{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VNYVd1Yl8yNk43amVBEAE","relativePublishTimeDescription":"8 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Our tenants' air conditioning unit unexpectedly stopped working late last night. We reached out to this company and had the pleasure of speaking directly with the owner, Danny. He responded with zero hesitation and scheduled a service appointment for the very next day.\nDanny the owner arrived early, was incredibly professional, and took the time to thoroughly explain the issue. He quickly diagnosed the problem and walked us through the cost before starting the repair. Not only was the price very reasonable, but his advice was honest and truly in our best interest.\nThis is the second time we've used Danny’s services, and we’ve been impressed both times. As a real estate agent with a large network of clients, I feel confident recommending Danny to anyone in need of air conditioning service. Reliable, honest, and efficient, exactly what you want in a professional!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Our tenants' air conditioning unit unexpectedly stopped working late last night. We reached out to this company and had the pleasure of speaking directly with the owner, Danny. He responded with zero hesitation and scheduled a service appointment for the very next day.\nDanny the owner arrived early, was incredibly professional, and took the time to thoroughly explain the issue. He quickly diagnosed the problem and walked us through the cost before starting the repair. Not only was the price very reasonable, but his advice was honest and truly in our best interest.\nThis is the second time we've used Danny’s services, and we’ve been impressed both times. As a real estate agent with a large network of clients, I feel confident recommending Danny to anyone in need of air conditioning service. Reliable, honest, and efficient, exactly what you want in a professional!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Nathalie Cantone","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104246130961922914898/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvm7jt_sQsZH3l-Re5kKgySnecF6t08j4r24AplfuGIb_g43ux=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2025-06-06T21:51:00.619509Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VNYVd1Yl8yNk43amVBEAE&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VNYVd1Yl8yNk43amVBEAE!2m1!1s0x89c24eb28c90bf0b:0xeb62d03ca65718c8"},{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZbHB6TTVBRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"9 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"It was 80 degrees on our house! I have young children and the heat was causing sleep issues. Danny was responsive and explained every detail down to the weather temperature best for repair. He is very punctual. He came with all equipment necessary for the job. The leak was found by using a special tool. Danny repaired the leak same day. My Central Air is running like it never had an issues. Thank You Danny our house is the perfect temperature & ready to take on these hot weather months!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"It was 80 degrees on our house! I have young children and the heat was causing sleep issues. Danny was responsive and explained every detail down to the weather temperature best for repair. He is very punctual. He came with all equipment necessary for the job. The leak was found by using a special tool. Danny repaired the leak same day. My Central Air is running like it never had an issues. Thank You Danny our house is the perfect temperature & ready to take on these hot weather months!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Regina Share","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110986408105362049602/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfcOpTAIvPOSy35wOeHAn3SdUgbjKK0Op9-OwEB22evTUpEbM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-05-04T02:47:21.894322Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZbHB6TTVBRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNZbHB6TTVBRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c24eb28c90bf0b:0xeb62d03ca65718c8"},{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VmEybHRMVVJpTkRVeFEzTmpiMWRGT1RsdFoxRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"7 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Danny was unbelievably quick and efficient with his work. He thoroughly explained what was going on with our system. Called him Saturday night and he was here bright and early Sunday morning, can not recommend NY heating & AC enough!!!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Danny was unbelievably quick and efficient with his work. He thoroughly explained what was going on with our system. Called him Saturday night and he was here bright and early Sunday morning, can not recommend NY heating & AC enough!!!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Sara Casanova","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118338634994373193425/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjLwsEajpSGqHWTSu_XltPzPMnnm32yzNTJMs3e8bkkAu7sg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-06-23T15:59:53.362143436Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VmEybHRMVVJpTkRVeFEzTmpiMWRGT1RsdFoxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VmEybHRMVVJpTkRVeFEzTmpiMWRGT1RsdFoxRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c24eb28c90bf0b:0xeb62d03ca65718c8"},{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNyNGVtZVBnEAE","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a year ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Great service and fair pricing. Danny was professional and thorough with his work. My particular central a/c installation was quite challenging with existing rusted out equipment. However, Danny worked quickly and with incredible focus while dealing with extreme heat and limited work space in my attic. The unit I have now works perfectly now. If you need fast, reliable service at a good price, I highly recommend Danny","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Great service and fair pricing. Danny was professional and thorough with his work. My particular central a/c installation was quite challenging with existing rusted out equipment. However, Danny worked quickly and with incredible focus while dealing with extreme heat and limited work space in my attic. The unit I have now works perfectly now. If you need fast, reliable service at a good price, I highly recommend Danny","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Gene","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111030886204612301328/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJK6fWhhHF4SJqb5pOZzLi4F07zS3_wxUk1dy7K5TF0UiQSFA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2024-07-08T04:29:54.806678Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNyNGVtZVBnEAE&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNyNGVtZVBnEAE!2m1!1s0x89c24eb28c90bf0b:0xeb62d03ca65718c8"}],"photos":[{"name":"places/ChIJC7-QjLJOwokRyBhXpjzQYus/photos/ATCDNfUosd5Mvb8lweX0HecVX_7SQXcZ0c6JJlMqluN_Nd5CbWdiNKpRRtw3hMqX0O71wO6CA8i-X14drI50zWrSvmqKpuw4-vjnhI_TDXA3psoMgMPDoE68o0i-1Pd9LJq3LSdpbFqyS-zJVRblFODg4UI0MwPpbb_X-DKDIM8AsRTBWwKCkZ_3So3m1Ty05ORVZYfUfrKr6HPeqzeTVNL26FavoZy1eLkmdlUh7JX9fknqWdBIyV7D3RrOGHZfRO34HACTMAnwCGo4EWveeBgMp6mUO254ekx6uZwMDmZxhCOjOw","widthPx":3024,"heightPx":4032,"authorAttributions":[{"displayName":"New York Heating and Air Conditioning","uri":"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/105429643784865472590","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZqQ61VRnqSrkQvlZrEj7SpdXw5X59eVP0l7Pp2YyWiHluoP0=s100-p-k-no-mo"}],"flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1zzUS6R5XvcBZa2m_tGuroaMesIz55VR8TNcp&hl=en-US","googleMapsUri":"https://www.